<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Sorry Diya ❤️</title>
<style>
    body {
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
        height: 100vh;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #fff;
        margin-top: 50px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #fff;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
    }

    .btn {
        padding: 12px 25px;
        font-size: 18px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin: 20px;
        position: absolute;
    }

    #yes {
        background-color: #28a745;
        color: white;
        left: 40%;
        top: 60%;
    }

    #no {
        background-color: #dc3545;
        color: white;
        left: 55%;
        top: 60%;
    }

    #message {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: white;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>I'm Sorry Diya 😔❤️ Meri Jaan</h1>

<p>
I know I made mistakes and hurt you... and I truly regret it.  
You mean a lot to me, more than I can explain.  
Please forgive me and give me one more chance to make things right 💙  
i dont know how to say i am boring yrr i dont have really so much of gossips to talk
so pls pls sorry and to say this i made this html code
</p>

<button id="yes" class="btn" onclick="yesClicked()">Yes 💖</button>
<button id="no" class="btn" onmouseover="moveNo()">No 😜</button>

<div id="message"></div>

<script>
function yesClicked() {
    document.getElementById("message").innerHTML = 
    "Yayyy!! 🥹❤️ Thank you for forgiving me sahiba (diya)! I promise I'll be better 💙";
}

function moveNo() {
    var noBtn = document.getElementById("no");
    var x = Math.random() * (window.innerWidth - 100);
    var y = Math.random() * (window.innerHeight - 50);

    noBtn.style.left = x + "px";
    noBtn.style.top = y + "px";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>